{
  "page": "Lord of Starfall",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of Starfall</b> is the title held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a>. It dates back to the time when Daynes ruled in their own right as <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Torentine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the Torentine\">Kings of the Torrentine</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_Starfall\">Known Lords of Starfall</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Starfall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of Starfall\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Dayne\" title=\"Samwell Dayne\">Samwell Dayne</a>, called the <i>Starfire</i></li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Vorian_Dayne\" title=\"Vorian Dayne\">Vorian Dayne</a>, called the <i>Sword of the Evening</i></li>\n<li>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Clarisse_Dayne\" title=\"Clarisse Dayne\">Clarisse Dayne</a>, Lady of Starfall</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Dayne_(father_of_Edric)\" title=\"Lord Dayne (father of Edric)\">Lord Dayne</a>, brother of <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Ashara_Dayne\" title=\"Ashara Dayne\">Ashara</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Allyria_Dayne\" title=\"Allyria Dayne\">Allyria</a>, and father of Edric.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafedric_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafedric_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edric_Dayne\" title=\"Edric Dayne\">Edric \"Ned\" Dayne</a>, the current Lord of Starfall<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Starfall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Kingdoms of the First Men.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafedric_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafedric_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Edric Dayne.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_43\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 43\">Chapter 43</a>, Arya VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404064750\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.015 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.016 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 239/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8618/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 998/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 232/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1569/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   10.895      1 -total\n 72.98%    7.951      3 Template:Ref\n 42.43%    4.623      3 Template:Ref/core\n 23.98%    2.613      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:21955-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404064750 and revision id 307346\n -->\n",
